You’re the greatest coach, role model a man could ask for! Thank you for everything! RUNNIN REBELS WHAT TIME IS IT!!!!!!! (If you know you know)  #rebel4life Love you Pops! #Legend #OG

My Baby Bestie turned Big 6! This sweet baby girl right here is the person who’s held my heart together through all of my bad times the past two years and I’m so grateful to have a daughter filled with so much love, laughter and grace! Without her huge heart and love I would be lost. So to make her happy on her big day me and Mommy made sure to give our Baby Bunny exactly what she wanted from the menu to the decorations and our little lady knew exactly what she wanted and she’s only 6 lol she’s been planning this out since she turned 5 lol! She had a blast with her friends and family and I’m happy she had the time of her life! Love you Muffin!! Happy Big 6!!!
